entries.title_d: Rescue the RSF Madersim which is listing in space
entries.title: Corellia System: Rescue the RSF Madersim
entries.thanks_5: Thank you for getting us out in once piece.
entries.thanks_4: Thank you for getting us out in once piece.
entries.thanks_3: I think it is a good day to retire.
entries.thanks_2: That was close Captain, you arrived just in time.
entries.thanks_1: Thank you for getting us out in once piece.
entries.rescue_phase_2: \#pcontrast3 Madersim: < \#pcontrast1 The repairs are sufficient to go, lets get out of here. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.rescue_phase_1: \#pcontrast3 Madersim: < \#pcontrast1 Hurry with those repairs, we need to get underway. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.recovery_success: \#pcontrast3 RSF Command: < \#pcontrast1 The mission is complete, return to base.  And great job out there today. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.quest_location_d: The secret escort route of the RSF Madersim
entries.quest_escort_d: Escort the repaired transport out of the zone
entries.quest_dock_d: Pull up next to the Madersim and use the /dock command
entries.panic_5: This is not looking very well.
entries.panic_4: This is not looking very well.
entries.panic_1: This is not looking very well.
entries.failed_destroy: \#pcontrast3 RSF Command: < \#pcontrast1 The Madersim has been destroyed, this is horrible. Return to base. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.docking_complete: Docking is complete, quick repairs beginning.
entries.complete: \#pcontrast3 RSF Command: < \#pcontrast1 The Madersim has successfully made their jump to hyperspace.  They are safe to complete their mission.  Time for you to return to base pilot. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.attack_stopped: \#pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < \#pcontrast1 The attack has stopped. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.attack_notify: \#pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < \#pcontrast1 Enemy craft detected on attack vector. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.arrival_phase_2: \#pcontrast3 Madersim: < \#pcontrast1 This is the RSF Madersim, we just escaped a heavy attack. Quickly dock to assist with repairs! \#pcontrast3 >
entries.arrival_phase_1: \#pcontrast3 RSF Command: < \#pcontrast1 We are locking down the Madersims' position.  Stand-by. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.abort: \#pcontrast3 Madersim: < \#pcontrast1 Where are you going, we cannot survive without you! \#pcontrast3 >
